*SHOP
T:Village Shop
A:The shopkeeper greets you.
A:"What can I get for you?"
A:1 - Buy a potion (10 gold)
A:2 - Buy a map (5 gold)
A:3 - Leave shop
A:
C:SHOP_CHOICE=#INPUT
A:
J:(SHOP_CHOICE=1)*BUY_POTION
J:(SHOP_CHOICE=2)*BUY_MAP
J:(SHOP_CHOICE=3)*LEAVE_SHOP
