J:*SHOP
A:
*BUY_MAP
J:(INVENTORY@*gold coin*)*BUY_MAP_OK
T:You don't have enough gold!
J:*SHOP
A:
*BUY_MAP_OK
T:You buy a map of the forest!
C:INVENTORY=INVENTORY + "map, "
