T:Mysterious Cave
A:It's dark and scary inside.
A:You hear a roar in the distance.
A:What do you do?
A:1 - Go deeper into the cave
A:2 - Use a potion if you have one
A:3 - Run away
A:
C:CAVE_CHOICE=#INPUT
A:
J:(CAVE_CHOICE=1)*GO_DEEPER
J:(CAVE_CHOICE=2)*USE_POTION
J:(CAVE_CHOICE=3)*RUN_FROM_CAVE
J:*INVALID_CAVE
